=== JADE_EMPEROR_STATUE ===
# id: 80
# title: The Jade Emperor
# chinese_title: 玉皇大帝
# category: Shrine
# mode: dungeon

A magnificent statue carved from what appears to be genuine jade towers over you. The Jade Emperor sits enthroned among holographic clouds, his expression serene. At his feet, offerings from many species have accumulated — tokens, crystals, written prayers.

* [Leave an offering and receive a blessing] {requires: gold >= 20}
  ~ gain_radical("玉")
  "玉" (yù) — jade, precious, pure
* [Read the written prayers of others]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "祈" (qí) — to pray, to wish
* [Examine the jade for authenticity]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "真" (zhēn) — real, genuine
* [Bow respectfully and move on]
  ~ heal(5)
  "拜" (bài) — to bow, to pay respects
